00:10:29,795 --> 00:10:33,049
{\an8}３･１４１５９２
６５３５８９７９…

175
00:10:33,049 --> 00:10:34,342
{\an8}３･１４１５９２
６５３５８９７９…

176
00:10:33,049 --> 00:10:34,342
